data.description: Magnificent luxury property that combines the tranquility of rural living w/the comfort of modern amenities. Situated on over 11 sprawling acres, this property offers a true oasis for those seeking a life of elegance, privacy, & space. Upon arriving at this country home, you'll be greeted by a front entry gate, & the property is fully fenced A& cross-fenced, making it an ideal space for horses, w/the potential to add more equestrian facilities. The front courtyard boasts custom accents & numerous seating areas, setting the stage for outdoor entertainment & relaxation. The meticulously landscaped grounds add to the charm of this exceptional property. The heart of this home is the well-appointed, open-concept kitchen. It features custom cherrywood cabinets, a spacious pantry, a built-in wine rack, stainless steel appliances, tile flooring, & custom quartz countertops accentuated by pendant lighting. The kitchen seamlessly opens to a cozy sitting area, & a nearby large formal dining area w/laminate flooring, complete w/a wood-burning stove, offers an ideal space for family gatherings and celebrations. The spacious living room is a luxurious haven for entertaining, with a gas fireplace adorned w/elegant curve accents. Spanish floor tiles, Venetian plaster walls, plantation shutters, & antique lighting add to the ambiance of this remarkable space. The executive suite is a private retreat of grand proportions, occupying its own wing of the home. W/its own exit to the rear patio, this suite includes a spacious ensuite bathroom w/dual sinks, a custom tile vanity backwall accent, an enormous walk-in closet, & a walk-in tile shower w/dual shower heads. The opposite wing of the home features 2 well-appointed guest bedrooms w/ample closet space & a guest bathroom. Step out to the backyard & be captivated by the stunning sunrise views of Mt Lassen. The expansive backyard offers ample space for family gatherings and outdoor activities. You'll also find a fully fenced garden area, perfect for cultivating your own produce. The home is equipped w/owned solar, on demand water heater & a lifetime metal roof. There's also an option to purchase a separate custom-built tiny home, which is already generating income through Airbnb. Detached from the home you will find an oversized finished garage w/a separate fully finished office. This exceptional property offers the luxury of country living, yet it's conveniently located close to town.
